# <type>(<optional-scope>): <description>
#
# [optional body — wyjaśnij co i dlaczego, nie jak]
#
# [optional footer — BREAKING CHANGE: opis, albo Co-Authored-By:]

# --- Types (release-please auto-bumps) ---
# feat:     nowy feature        → minor bump (0.1 → 0.2)
# fix:      bug fix             → patch bump (0.1.0 → 0.1.1)
# feat!:    BREAKING            → w 0.x: minor; w 1.x+: major
# BREAKING CHANGE: (w body)     → j.w.
#
# --- Types (non-release, no bump) ---
# docs:     dokumentacja
# chore:    nudne rzeczy (deps, configs)
# refactor: reorganizacja bez zmiany behavior
# test:     testy
# ci:       CI/CD
# style:    formatting, whitespace
# perf:     performance bez zmiany behavior
#
# --- Przykłady ---
# feat(models): add CaseStudy model with Filament Resource
# fix(sitemap): handle null updated_at on Pages
# feat!: rename Lead::status to Lead::stage
# chore(deps): bump phpstan to 3.0
#
# Enable template: git config commit.template .gitmessage
